              This app will allow users to create and maintain a Tango collection of Tango playlists.
            </p>
            <div class="buttons">
              <button class="ui orange button">
                Introduce yourself <i class="question mark icon"></i>
              </button>
              <button class="ui yellow button">
                Info <i class="info icon"></i>
              </button>
              <button class="ui blue button">
                Like us!  <i class=" heart icon"></i>
              </button>
            </div>
          <div id="info" class="ui message">
            <p>
              So far, there is CRUD (Create, Read, Update, and Delete) functionality running in this app. In the future, users will also be able to create an account, log in and upload images to this app.
            </p>  
          </div>
          <div id="introduction" class="ui message"> </div>
        
        <div class="ui divider"></div>

